org.lafayette.server.mapper
Class BaseStatementSource

java.lang.Object
  org.lafayette.server.mapper.BaseStatementSource
All Implemented Interfaces:
StatementSource
abstract class BaseStatementSource
extends Object
implements StatementSource

Base implementation for a statement source. Prepare a statement source: 

 executePreparedStatement(new BaseStatementSource() {

      @Override public String sql() {
          return "select foo, bar, baz from snafu where id = ?";
      }

      @Override public Object[] parameters() {
          return new Object[]{ Integer.valueOf(23) };
      }
 });
Use a statement source: 
 PreparedStatement stmt = source.prepare(db);
 ResultSet rs = stmt.executeQuery();
The parameters will be set in the same order on the prepared statement as they occurs in the parameters array.

Author:
Sven Strittmatter
